                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for selectively removing chloride ions by electrochemical working unit",
                    "一种电化学工作单元选择性去除氯离子的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for selectively removing chloride ions by an electrochemical working unit, which utilizes the electrochemical action of metal bismuth and chloride ions to form a Bi/BiOCl reversible electrode pair, can effectively realize the selective removal of chloride ions, and keeps the acidity and alkalinity of a product solution and a concentrated solution unchanged. The problem that acid or alkali needs to be additionally and continuously added to keep the acid-alkali neutrality of the final product liquid and the concentrated liquid is avoided, and the production and operation cost is reduced; the acid-base property of a product liquid and a concentrated solution of the first electrochemical working unit is changed by a method for reversely generating hydrogen ions and hydroxyl ions by electrolyzing water through a bipolar membrane catalyst layer in the first electrochemical working unit, and the product liquid and the concentrated solution of the first electrochemical working unit are subjected to acid-base neutralization with a product liquid and a concentrated solution of the second electrochemical working unit; therefore, the acid-base property of the final product liquid and the concentrated liquid is neutral."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种电化学工作单元选择性去除氯离子的方法，该方法利用金属铋与氯离子的电化学作用形成Bi/BiOCl可逆电极对，能有效地实现氯离子的选择性去除，并且保持了产品液和浓缩液的酸碱性不发生变化，避免了要额外不断加入酸或碱以保持最终产品液和浓缩液的酸碱中性问题，降低了生产运行成本；通过第一电化学工作单元中的双极膜催化层电解水反向产生氢离子和氢氧根离子的方法，改变第一电化学工作单元产品液和浓缩液的酸碱性，与第二电化学工作单元的产品液和浓缩液进行酸碱中和，从而使最终的产品液和浓缩液的酸碱性为中性。"
                }
            ]
